<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nouveau transport disponible</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 180px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .transport-info {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #4a90e2;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .detail-row {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #555;
        }
        .value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #4a90e2;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: #3a80d2;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="cid:logo" alt="TerraNav Logo">
            <h1>Nouveau Transport Disponible!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Bonjour {{ user.prenom }},</p>
            
            <p>Une agence de transport sur TerraNav a ajouté un nouveau service de transport qui pourrait vous intéresser:</p>
            
            <div class="transport-info">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Nom du transport:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ transport.nom }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Type:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ transport.type }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Capacité:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ transport.capacite }} personnes</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Prix:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ transport.prix }} DTN</span>
                </div>
                {% if trajet %}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Départ:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ trajet.pointDepart }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Destination:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ trajet.destination }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Date de départ:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ trajet.dateDepart|date('d/m/Y H:i') }}</span>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                {% if transport.description %}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Description:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ transport.description }}</span>
                </div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="label">Contact:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ transport.contact }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>Vous pouvez réserver ce transport directement sur notre site en cliquant sur le bouton ci-dessous:</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="http://localhost:8000/client/transport/{{ transport.id }}" class="button">Voir le transport</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>Nous espérons que vous trouverez ce transport adapté à vos besoins.</p>
            
            <p>Merci de voyager avec TerraNav!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© {{ "now"|date('Y') }} TerraNav. Tous droits réservés.</p>
            <p>Cet email a été envoyé à {{ user.email }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>